Subject: [PATCH] vendor(openclaw): bridge Feishu business form cards

Why:
- Desktop needs trusted raw form-card sends and complete form callbacks without dispatching an agent.

Removal:
- Drop when bundled Feishu supports policy-aware namespaced form callbacks and trusted raw Schema 2.0 sends.

